    <section id="introduction">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to our guide on achieving good health and well-being. This page provides information and tips to help you lead a healthier and happier life.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="physical-health">
        <h2>Physical Health</h2>
        <p>Physical health involves taking care of your body through proper nutrition, regular exercise, and adequate rest.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="mental-health">
        <h2>Mental Health</h2>
        <p>Mental health is just as important as physical health. It includes managing stress, practicing mindfulness, and seeking support when needed.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="nutrition">
        <h2>Nutrition</h2>
        <p>A balanced diet is crucial for good health. Include plenty of fruits, vegetables, lean proteins, and whole grains in your meals.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="exercise">
        <h2>Exercise</h2>
        <p>Regular physical activity can improve your mood, boost your energy levels, and reduce the risk of chronic diseases. Aim for at least 30 minutes of moderate exercise most days of the week.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="tips">
        <h2>Tips for Well-being</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Get enough sleep</li>
            <li>Stay hydrated</li>
            <li>Practice mindfulness</li>
            <li>Connect with others</li>
            <li>Engage in hobbies</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

